h3. Steps to reproduce

# Create an user at JIRA;
# Create a new SD Project;
# Edit this username in a way to add his email address. For example:
{noformat}
old username: john
new username: john@isntance.atlassian.net
{noformat}
# Assign the SD user role to this new user.
# Create a ticket and assign it to this new user.
# On Workload of SD Project, click at the "Issues in progress" to see the issues of this new user. 

h3. Current behaviour

The JQL won't bring any results.


h3. Expected behaviour

The JQL should return this user's issue .

