As an Admin It would be nice to be able to customize the Text in the Service Desk Default Customer Portal Base Page Search Box:
- https://<INSTANCE_NAME>.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portals

Text to customize: {{What do you need help with?}}

h3. Suggested Solution
Add ability to customize text or disable fully

